get.description:
Returns geostore based on a single ID, if the geostore not exist return 404
### Example URL request
```
{{host}}/geostore/ca38fa80a4ffa9ac6217a7e0bf71e6df
```
### Example response
* Saving a geojson
```json
{
      "data": {
          "type": "geoStore",
          "id": "ca38fa80a4ffa9ac6217a7e0bf71e6df",
          "attributes": {
              "geojson": {
                  "features": [{
                      "type": "Feature",
                      "geometry": {
                          "type": "Polygon",
                          "coordinates": [
                              [
                                  [-5.273512601852417,
                                      42.81137220349083
                                  ],
                                  [-5.273512601852417,
                                      42.811803118457306
                                  ],
                                  [-5.272732079029083,
                                      42.811803118457306
                                  ],
                                  [-5.272732079029083,
                                      42.81137220349083
                                  ],
                                  [-5.273512601852417,
                                      42.81137220349083
                                  ]
                              ]
                          ]
                      }
                  }],
                  "crs": {},
                  "type": "FeatureCollection"
              },
              "hash": "ca38fa80a4ffa9ac6217a7e0bf71e6df",
              "provider": {},
              "areaHa": 0.3057556230214663
          }
      }
  }
```

post.description:
### 2 posibilities to create geostore

* Send geojson in a body (geojson attribute)
* Send provider object with all params. With this mode, the geostore obtain the geojson in the provider. Support providers-> carto

### Example response
* Saving a geojson
```json
{
      "data": {
          "type": "geoStore",
          "id": "ca38fa80a4ffa9ac6217a7e0bf71e6df",
          "attributes": {
              "geojson": {
                  "features": [{
                      "type": "Feature",
                      "geometry": {
                          "type": "Polygon",
                          "coordinates": [
                              [
                                  [-5.273512601852417,
                                      42.81137220349083
                                  ],
                                  [-5.273512601852417,
                                      42.811803118457306
                                  ],
                                  [-5.272732079029083,
                                      42.811803118457306
                                  ],
                                  [-5.272732079029083,
                                      42.81137220349083
                                  ],
                                  [-5.273512601852417,
                                      42.81137220349083
                                  ]
                              ]
                          ]
                      }
                  }],
                  "crs": {},
                  "type": "FeatureCollection"
              },
              "hash": "ca38fa80a4ffa9ac6217a7e0bf71e6df",
              "provider": {},
              "areaHa": 0.3057556230214663
          }
      }
  }
```
